<subSubSection pageId="42" pageNumber="43" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="42.[151,1436,253,496]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,325,351]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Remarks.</emphasis>
In 
<bibRefCitation author="Lobato-Vila, I. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J." box="[353,649,325,352]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" pagination="341 - 362" refId="ref46693" refString="Lobato-Vila, I., Wang, Y., Melika, G., Guo, R., Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. (2021 a) A review of the species in the genus Synergus Hartig (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from mainland China, with an updated key to Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental species. Journal of Asia-Pacific Entomology, 24 (1), 341 - 362. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. aspen. 2020.11.014" type="journal article" year="2021">
Lobato-Vila 
<emphasis box="[496,545,325,351]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">et al</emphasis>
. (2021a)
</bibRefCitation>
, new material of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Uchida &amp; Sakagami" authorityYear="1948" box="[844,974,326,352]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Synergus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jezoensis">
<emphasis box="[844,974,326,352]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">S. jezoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[1043,1110,325,351]" name="China" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">China</collectingCountry>
was identified as originating from galls of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Yasumatsu &amp; Masuda" authorityYear="1955" baseAuthorityName="Mukaigawa" baseAuthorityYear="1913" box="[303,553,361,387]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Andricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mukaigawae">
<emphasis box="[303,553,361,387]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Andricus mukaigawae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on 
<taxonomicName box="[594,683,361,388]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fabri">
<emphasis box="[594,683,361,388]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Q. fabri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see Remarks for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1874" box="[888,1025,362,388]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Synergus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="japonicus">
<emphasis box="[888,1025,362,388]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">S. japonicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="42.[151,1436,253,496]" box="[151,1322,397,424]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,307,397,423]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Remarks (2).</emphasis>
Redescribed and illustrated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Pujade-Villar, J. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Chen, X. &amp; He, J." box="[661,969,397,424]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" pagination="534 - 544" refId="ref51167" refString="Pujade-Villar, J., Wang, Y., Chen, X. &amp; He, J. (2014 b) Taxonomic review of East Palearctic species of Synergus section I, with description of a new species from China (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipinae). Zoological Systematics, 39 (4), 534 - 544. https: // doi. org / 10.11865 / j. zs. 20140406" type="journal article" year="2014">
Pujade-Villar 
<emphasis box="[817,866,397,423]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">et al</emphasis>
. (2014b)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Lobato-Vila, I. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J." box="[1023,1318,397,424]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" pagination="341 - 362" refId="ref46693" refString="Lobato-Vila, I., Wang, Y., Melika, G., Guo, R., Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. (2021 a) A review of the species in the genus Synergus Hartig (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from mainland China, with an updated key to Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental species. Journal of Asia-Pacific Entomology, 24 (1), 341 - 362. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. aspen. 2020.11.014" type="journal article" year="2021">
Lobato-Vila 
<emphasis box="[1165,1214,397,423]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">et al</emphasis>
. (2021a)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="42" pageNumber="43" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="42.[151,1436,253,496]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,295,433,459]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Biology.</emphasis>
Reared from galls of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Yasumatsu &amp; Masuda" authorityYear="1955" baseAuthorityName="Mukaigawa" baseAuthorityYear="1913" box="[534,783,433,459]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Andricus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mukaigawae">
<emphasis box="[534,783,433,459]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Andricus mukaigawae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(generation unknown) presumably on 
<taxonomicName box="[1211,1298,433,460]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fabri">
<emphasis box="[1211,1231,434,460]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Q</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1244,1298,433,459]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">fabri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sect. 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">Quercus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) (see Remarks above) (Table 2; 
<bibRefCitation author="Lobato-Vila, I. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J." box="[554,832,469,496]" pageId="42" pageNumber="43" pagination="341 - 362" refId="ref46693" refString="Lobato-Vila, I., Wang, Y., Melika, G., Guo, R., Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. (2021 a) A review of the species in the genus Synergus Hartig (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from mainland China, with an updated key to Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental species. Journal of Asia-Pacific Entomology, 24 (1), 341 - 362. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. aspen. 2020.11.014" type="journal article" year="2021">
Lobato-Vila 
<emphasis box="[696,745,469,495]" italics="true" pageId="42" pageNumber="43">et al</emphasis>
. 2021a
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
